---
title: Carb Smart Beyond Meat® and Brussels Sprouts Salad with Apples and Dijon Dressing
description: This carb smart Beyond Meat® and Brussels sprouts salad features hearty Dijon and sweet apples! You won't miss the starch in this supper.

